      • process

        public boolean process(java.lang.String cmd,
                       CommandSender sender,
                       DarwinLocation loc)
        Attempt to process the given command for the CommandSender. If no appropriate command is present false will be returned, in any other case true is returned.
        Parameters:
        cmd - The command to execute, without a preceding slash
        sender - The command sender, usually a player, console or commandblock
        loc - The location of the sender, if this is a non-player sender the location should be empty
        Returns:
        whether or not the command was processed by the command bus
